&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17482&quot; title=&quot;short read does not set ki_pos correctly&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-17482&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-17482&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; llite: short read could mess up next read offset&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When read reaches EOF, it could read data from stale pagecache, but&lt;br/&gt;
we need to restore the iocb-&amp;gt;ki_pos so that next read could continue&lt;br/&gt;
from the correct offset.&lt;/p&gt;
